snippet.title: Miss Input 2 Deathless (Amstrad CPC Homebrew) (RetroAchievements)
snippet.description: Since I did this for the first one, thought I do the second one as well. I feel this one is way easier than the first, just some small spots that are a little finicky. The bouncy gravity with projectiles has a nice cycle in the beginning if you can hit it (I got it but almost messed it up), makes it more consistent to get through.
